rComments: Gary teaches a few KIN courses and he knows what he is talking about; so he likes to talk about it A LOT. If you get over this you can enjoy the course and he's a pretty chill guy. If you try and have issues he's an easy grader and understands; if I had to choose between Gary and someone else it'd always be Gary.
Gary is a nice guy. The class is very clear and you have 3 tests and a presentation. Not bad at all.
